data.description: Nicely updated 4 bedroom, 2 bathroom home that sits on a large lot. This home showcases beautiful bamboo floors throughout the main level. The updated kitchen features granite counters, cinnamon cherry cabinetry, custom tile backsplash, under cabinet lighting and stainless steel appliances. The attached dining area has built in cabinetry for additional storage. There are three bedrooms and an updated bathroom with granite counters, nice vanity and custom tile tub surround on the main level. The huge master suite is located on the lower level. It has a professionally organized walk-in closet and updated master bathroom featuring a glass enclosed walk-in shower with custom tile. Relax in the theater/family room with a home cinema projector and large screen or unwind in the sunroom off of the kitchen with great views of the private back yard. There is plenty of space in the 2-1/2 car garage and extra storage in the shed behind the garage. This home has been well maintained! Great location close to expressway, shopping and within close proximity to elementary school and park. Call today to schedule your private showing!
